long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension lets you log all the keystrokes you enter on various websites and saves them in a secure remote database with AES encryption.

PLEASE RESTART THE BROWSER FOR CHANGES TO TAKE EFFECT 

Each User has its own unique UUID that is created when the app runs for the first time and your data can be accessed anywhere on web, using the API key that you created.
Your keylogs can be accessed here:
https://spykeys.vercel.app

The data that is saved in the database is encrypted using Advanced Encryption Standard (AES), so no one can have access to it even in case of a breach.

You have complete access to your data stored in SpyKeys and it can all be removed with one click on "Delete Data" button.
